!!! 忽略空气阻力的情况

```wl
h = 10000;
g = 9.8;
Sqrt[2*h/g]
```
```
45.1754
```

!!! 考虑空气阻力的情况

```wl
m = 75;
c = 1;
a = 0.5;
\[Rho][h_] := 1.225 Exp[-h/9000]
```

```wl
r = NDSolve[{m y''[t] == m g - 1/2 c*a*\[Rho][h - y[t]] y'[t]^2, y[0] == 0, y'[0] == 0}, y, {t, 0, 600}]
ry = y /. r[[1]]
rt = FindRoot[ry[t] == h, {t, 10}]
tm = t /. rt
```
```
160.798
```

```wl
Plot[{h - ry[t], h - 1/2 g t^2}, {t, 0, tm}, 
 PlotRange -> {All, {0, h}},
 FrameLabel -> {"时间/秒", "高度/米"}, 
 PlotLegends -> 
  Placed[LineLegend[{"考虑空气阻力", "忽略空气阻力"}, 
    LegendFunction -> (Framed[#1, FrameMargins -> 0] &)], {Right, Top}],
 PlotTheme -> "Scientific"
 ]
